    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1753972608\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Clawed Cult: 一款反向弹幕地狱冒险游戏！</h2><br>进入 Clawed Cult 的奇异世界，在这里，可爱的动物崇拜古老的邪恶神灵 Catchulhu。作为一个邪教徒，你必须穿过由以前失败的召唤仪式形成的敌人大军，使用强大的武器和巧妙的策略来生存活下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/91d12fef9b65d5caf742b9b0eb1ac04d.poster.avif?t=1753972608\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/91d12fef9b65d5caf742b9b0eb1ac04d.webm?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/91d12fef9b65d5caf742b9b0eb1ac04d.mp4?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>控制混乱，向敌人倾泻毁灭性打击，同时躲避他们的攻击。随着你的进展，你将召唤并与更大更可怕的生物战斗，以便利用它们的力量来呼唤你的长者神。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/695f19e26ef5b0fa62e167a8314f748d.poster.avif?t=1753972608\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/695f19e26ef5b0fa62e167a8314f748d.webm?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/695f19e26ef5b0fa62e167a8314f748d.mp4?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你能否掌握反向弹幕地狱的艺术并召唤 Catchulhu？只有最勇敢和最狡猾的邪教徒才能在古老神灵的荣耀中幸存下来！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Clawed Cult 特点：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 反向弹幕地狱机制，带来独特而具有挑战性的游戏体验； <br></li><li> 可爱而诡异的邪教动物，每个都有自己独特的能力和武器； <br></li><li> 充满神秘和古老生物的洛夫克拉夫特世界； <br></li><li> 召唤你击败过的首领来帮助你进入战斗； <br></li><li> 成群结队的敌人，每个都有自己的攻击模式和能力； <br></li><li> 可升级武器和能力，让你在进展中变得更加强大； <br></li><li> 自适应音乐：每次听到新配乐时都与你的游戏节奏相匹配！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/4c68ac4b687a9c9dad1c6a5f0452dba6.poster.avif?t=1753972608\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/4c68ac4b687a9c9dad1c6a5f0452dba6.webm?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385630/extras/4c68ac4b687a9c9dad1c6a5f0452dba6.mp4?t=1753972608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>加入邪教，在 Clawed Cult 中体验反向弹幕地狱的刺激！",
